205
00:16:45,761 --> 00:16:47,871
What? Her husband?

206
00:16:48,170 --> 00:16:50,731
- They are married? - This is unbelievable.

207
00:16:51,001 --> 00:16:52,741
How could this be?

208
00:17:00,381 --> 00:17:02,150
The Princess is married?

209
00:17:03,751 --> 00:17:06,151
It is too early to be dreaming.

210
00:17:06,151 --> 00:17:07,721
I am not making this up.

211
00:17:07,991 --> 00:17:10,620
A eunuch rushing from the hall told me.

212
00:17:10,751 --> 00:17:13,961
The Princess appeared with a young man at her side...

213
00:17:13,961 --> 00:17:16,661
and announced they are already married.

214
00:17:16,661 --> 00:17:17,901
That is nonsense.

215
00:17:17,901 --> 00:17:20,100
Then go to the hall yourself.

216
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:22,300
It was turned upside-down.

217
00:17:23,501 --> 00:17:24,771
What...

218
00:17:33,981 --> 00:17:36,211
This is not your fortune.

219
00:17:36,810 --> 00:17:39,481
Whose fate is it you wish to learn of?

220
00:17:39,681 --> 00:17:41,921
You really are as good as rumours say.

221
00:17:42,521 --> 00:17:44,390
You have such great skill,

222
00:17:44,691 --> 00:17:47,021
so what did you do before you came to the Capital?

223
00:17:47,691 --> 00:17:48,691
She is leaving.

224
00:17:48,691 --> 00:17:51,030
I would like to hear my fortune before I am thrown out.

225
00:17:52,761 --> 00:17:54,870
Did you see that person's future?

226
00:17:57,300 --> 00:18:00,001
Corpses are stacked as high as mountains,

227
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:04,880
and blood flows like a river.

228
00:18:06,080 --> 00:18:09,481
Starved wild dogs gather from all around,

229
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,550
and there is nowhere to flee.

230
00:18:12,251 --> 00:18:15,021
This karma can only be atoned for with death.

231
00:18:15,721 --> 00:18:17,151
What a pity.

232
00:18:17,590 --> 00:18:19,491
A fate that is unavoidable.

233
00:18:20,120 --> 00:18:22,290
A fate that is cursed.

234
00:18:23,530 --> 00:18:26,161
When I had lost my memory and was wandering,

235
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:28,231
he showed me the way...

236
00:18:28,671 --> 00:18:30,600
and allowed me to rely on him.

237
00:18:32,441 --> 00:18:34,201
His unchanging heart...

238
00:18:34,971 --> 00:18:36,711
is what moved me.

239
00:18:39,181 --> 00:18:42,411
You asked me to release a young man from prison.

240
00:18:42,681 --> 00:18:45,050
You said he had saved your life many times.

241
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:49,350
Was that this man?

242
00:18:49,991 --> 00:18:51,290
Yes.

243
00:18:51,890 --> 00:18:55,431
At the time, you clearly said he was a friend.

244
00:18:55,931 --> 00:18:59,501
And yet now you say he is your husband.

245
00:19:00,300 --> 00:19:02,070
Are you insulting me?

246
00:19:02,171 --> 00:19:04,600
Father. It is not like that.

247
00:19:04,701 --> 00:19:05,800
Shut your mouth.

248
00:19:08,110 --> 00:19:09,441
Please calm down.

249
00:19:09,671 --> 00:19:13,110
I believe the Princess is scheming to avoid her marriage.

250
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:14,981
Yes.

251
00:19:16,610 --> 00:19:18,481
You are already married?

252
00:19:18,681 --> 00:19:22,350
That is very hard to believe, Your Highness.

253
00:19:26,921 --> 00:19:28,890
How else do we say what has been done?

254
00:19:30,161 --> 00:19:32,100
- What? - How dare you?

255
00:19:32,461 --> 00:19:33,461
I am...

256
00:19:35,100 --> 00:19:36,701
the Princess' husband.

257
00:19:40,241 --> 00:19:41,911
You are out of your mind!

258
00:19:41,911 --> 00:19:43,870
How dare you raise your voice here?

259
00:19:43,870 --> 00:19:46,241
You sneaked into the palace under an assumed identity!

260
00:19:47,780 --> 00:19:49,981
That is very true.

261
00:19:49,981 --> 00:19:52,221
We cannot accept a man of unclear identity...

262
00:19:52,221 --> 00:19:54,620
and status as the Princess' spouse.

263
00:19:54,620 --> 00:19:55,991
Your Majesty.

264
00:19:55,991 --> 00:19:58,120
- Your Majesty. - Your Majesty.

265
00:20:02,931 --> 00:20:05,100
What is your name?

266
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:18,011
My father was Daemodal...

267
00:20:18,741 --> 00:20:20,310
and a Widudehyeong.

268
00:20:20,310 --> 00:20:21,550
(Widudehyeong: A 5th Grade rank)

269
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:24,481
I am the son of General On Hyeop, the 17th chief of the Sunno Tribe,

270
00:20:26,820 --> 00:20:28,221
My name is On Dal.

271
00:20:28,651 --> 00:20:29,991
On Hyeop's son?

272
00:20:30,820 --> 00:20:31,991
What?

273
00:20:40,931 --> 00:20:42,671
Long time no see, Hyeop.

274
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:45,540
If you admit that you are a traitor,

275
00:20:46,070 --> 00:20:48,040
I will spare the lives of everyone else.

276
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:03,320
My goodness.

277
00:21:07,421 --> 00:21:10,761
You are actually the son of On Hyeop?

278
00:21:11,731 --> 00:21:12,931
That is true.

279
00:21:14,431 --> 00:21:15,501
Yes.

280
00:21:16,370 --> 00:21:18,501
I remember that gaze.

281
00:21:19,471 --> 00:21:21,070
You take after your father.

282
00:21:22,140 --> 00:21:23,971
On Hyeop...

283
00:21:24,441 --> 00:21:27,441
was beheaded for committing treason.

284
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:30,350
The reason his family...

285
00:21:30,350 --> 00:21:32,451
and the remaining people of the tribe...

286
00:21:32,451 --> 00:21:35,221
were allowed to live was by the King's grace.

287
00:21:35,390 --> 00:21:36,921
He forgot about all that...

288
00:21:37,491 --> 00:21:40,360
and entered the palace, causing this fuss.

289
00:21:40,421 --> 00:21:43,790
He must be severely punished!

290
00:21:43,890 --> 00:21:45,130
That is correct.

291
00:21:45,431 --> 00:21:48,070
Please punish him severely.

292
00:21:48,201 --> 00:21:49,431
Punish him?

293
00:21:49,431 --> 00:21:51,070
They may have married in secret,

294
00:21:51,070 --> 00:21:53,001
but he is the Princess' husband.

295
00:21:53,401 --> 00:21:55,540
Must he be dealt a severe penalty?

296
00:21:56,411 --> 00:21:59,681
Your Majesty. You must not do anything to harm your authority.

297
00:21:59,681 --> 00:22:02,911
Having a royal marry someone from that bloodline...

298
00:22:02,911 --> 00:22:05,820
already harms the royal household's authority!

299
00:22:05,921 --> 00:22:07,421
Your Majesty.

300
00:22:07,651 --> 00:22:09,790
- Your Majesty. - Your Majesty.

301
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:11,120
Silence!

302
00:22:31,441 --> 00:22:32,741
Your Majesty.

303
00:22:32,981 --> 00:22:33,981
Your Majesty.

304
00:22:34,140 --> 00:22:36,580
- My goodness. - What is happening?

305
00:22:37,711 --> 00:22:40,080
You did nothing but cause trouble since you returned,

306
00:22:40,421 --> 00:22:42,691
and you ended up bringing disgrace on your father.

307
00:22:43,021 --> 00:22:44,890
- Father. - Shut your mouth!

308
00:22:45,390 --> 00:22:47,590
You are no longer my daughter.

309
00:22:48,130 --> 00:22:50,261
Leave the palace immediately.

310
00:22:54,870 --> 00:22:57,300
I will accept any punishment. The Princess...

311
00:22:57,300 --> 00:22:58,800
Did you not hear me?

312
00:23:00,840 --> 00:23:04,171
I no longer have a daughter.

313
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:07,840
The next time I see you,

314
00:23:09,651 --> 00:23:12,221
I will behead you both on the spot.

315
00:24:05,401 --> 00:24:06,401
Are you all right?

316
00:24:49,050 --> 00:24:50,050
My lady.

317
00:24:51,251 --> 00:24:54,350
The Princess was ordered to leave the palace.

318
00:24:55,221 --> 00:24:56,221
She must leave?

319
00:25:17,411 --> 00:25:18,540
I am sorry, Nanny.

320
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:21,610
I am leaving after causing you much distress.

321
00:25:23,580 --> 00:25:25,280
You are not married.

322
00:25:26,421 --> 00:25:29,850
Tell the King that you lied. Please?

323
00:25:30,951 --> 00:25:32,661
Do you not believe it either?

324
00:25:34,060 --> 00:25:37,060
I cared for you even before you could murmur.

325
00:25:38,130 --> 00:25:40,931
Do you think I do not see through you?

326
00:25:43,431 --> 00:25:47,300
I would rather leave the palace with you.

327
00:25:47,570 --> 00:25:49,241
I will look after you and...

328
00:25:49,241 --> 00:25:52,580
No. You must protect my brother Won.

329
00:25:56,580 --> 00:25:59,251
You are the only person I can entrust...

330
00:25:59,850 --> 00:26:01,151
his safety.

331
00:26:02,521 --> 00:26:04,850
Oh, dear...

332
00:26:27,741 --> 00:26:29,751
Are you the man my sister married?

333
00:26:30,050 --> 00:26:31,850
Oh, the Crown Prince?

334
00:26:40,421 --> 00:26:41,421
Crown Prince.

335
00:26:42,691 --> 00:26:44,330
Are you really leaving?

336
00:26:44,491 --> 00:26:46,100
Leaving me on my own?

337
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:48,501
Father is so furious.

338
00:26:49,070 --> 00:26:50,671
I have no choice.

339
00:26:50,800 --> 00:26:52,271
You must beg.

340
00:26:52,671 --> 00:26:54,171
Ask him to forgive you.

341
00:26:54,971 --> 00:26:56,810
Beg to let him allow you to stay.

342
00:26:57,271 --> 00:26:58,780
If you leave again,

343
00:26:59,340 --> 00:27:00,610
what do I do alone?

344
00:27:01,610 --> 00:27:03,880
You might never be able to return this time.

345
00:27:09,620 --> 00:27:10,751
I will return.

346
00:27:11,721 --> 00:27:15,630
For you and  Father, I will come back.

347
00:27:18,530 --> 00:27:22,001
You and Father both. I hate you.

348
00:27:23,530 --> 00:27:24,630
I hate you all.

349
00:27:25,471 --> 00:27:26,671
Do not say that.

350
00:27:27,771 --> 00:27:31,171
Father is trying to save my life.

351
00:27:33,040 --> 00:27:36,481
This is the only way I can avoid the royal wedding.

352
00:27:37,810 --> 00:27:41,481
Father gave the order but he is crying inside.

353
00:27:44,850 --> 00:27:47,491
The Princess came to say goodbye.

354
00:27:47,590 --> 00:27:49,860
Are you out of your mind?

355
00:27:52,961 --> 00:27:55,171
There is no princess in this family.

356
00:28:00,001 --> 00:28:03,211
You must leave without seeing your father.

357
00:28:04,640 --> 00:28:05,741
Father.

358
00:28:07,110 --> 00:28:08,981
Do you hear me?

359
00:28:10,780 --> 00:28:12,820
I am leaving the palace.

360
00:28:16,590 --> 00:28:19,620
I wish more than anything to remain here with you,

361
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:23,860
but accepting your command is also my filial duty.

362
00:28:24,731 --> 00:28:26,401
So I shall leave.

363
00:28:30,100 --> 00:28:31,100
Until now,

364
00:28:32,241 --> 00:28:34,140
I did nothing but cause you concern.

365
00:28:36,040 --> 00:28:37,411
Please forgive me.

366
00:28:43,550 --> 00:28:45,221
Do not worry!

367
00:28:46,280 --> 00:28:49,491
I will protect the Princess.

368
00:29:17,441 --> 00:29:19,941
You have made a very difficult decision.

369
00:29:20,281 --> 00:29:22,281
Since the Princess has left,

370
00:29:23,210 --> 00:29:25,480
the palace will finally find peace.

371
00:29:27,050 --> 00:29:30,491
Are you happy about that?

372
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:34,531
Of course not.

373
00:29:35,491 --> 00:29:39,360
I only wish for peace and safety in the palace.

374
00:29:41,870 --> 00:29:43,201
If you have any regrets,

375
00:29:44,171 --> 00:29:46,601
you can always tell the Princess to come back.

376
00:30:01,890 --> 00:30:04,621
How could he kick you out like this when you are a princess?

377
00:30:06,390 --> 00:30:09,561
He is so mean. He did not even see you out.

378
00:30:10,491 --> 00:30:11,561
Dal.

379
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:15,130
I need to stop by somewhere.

380
00:30:15,770 --> 00:30:16,931
Where?

381
00:30:17,031 --> 00:30:19,640
I will be right back, so you should go ahead first and wait there.

382
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:21,041
Let us meet at the entrance of Mungyeongsaejae.

383
00:30:21,041 --> 00:30:23,270
You are going alone? Let me tag along.

384
00:30:23,270 --> 00:30:24,580
Do not worry.

385
00:30:24,580 --> 00:30:27,481
From now on, we will always be together.

386
00:30:33,921 --> 00:30:35,121
Make sure to come back fast!

387
00:30:41,261 --> 00:30:43,830
I was surprised when I heard that you are already married.

388
00:30:44,600 --> 00:30:46,901
And you had to be kicked out of the palace all of a sudden.

389
00:30:47,500 --> 00:30:49,871
I do not know how to console you.

390
00:30:49,871 --> 00:30:51,300
You need not say anything.

391
00:30:52,371 --> 00:30:53,770
I am here to ask for your help.

392
00:30:55,841 --> 00:30:57,981
It is a waste to take you as my enemy,

393
00:30:58,880 --> 00:31:01,651
but I cannot fully trust you to have you on my side.

394
00:31:01,850 --> 00:31:03,981
But you came to see me nonetheless.

395
00:31:04,981 --> 00:31:06,951
That must mean that you want to put trust in me.

396
00:31:07,651 --> 00:31:09,921
I also wanted to know why you helped me.

397
00:31:11,360 --> 00:31:15,190
I know you are good at figures, and you have nothing to gain from this.

398
00:31:15,761 --> 00:31:19,130
Do you remember what I have told you?

399
00:31:20,130 --> 00:31:21,500
I...

400
00:31:23,271 --> 00:31:25,641
abhor Go Won Pyo.

401
00:31:26,940 --> 00:31:29,341
I may not resent him as much as you do,

402
00:31:31,040 --> 00:31:32,781
but I want to protect...

403
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:35,111
the tribe my father has been keeping, the Sono Tribe,

404
00:31:36,051 --> 00:31:37,950
even though I am his step-daughter.

405
00:31:38,220 --> 00:31:41,450
Then you should help me.

406
00:31:43,021 --> 00:31:46,361
Let us stop the Gyeru Tribe from abusing their power,

407
00:31:47,630 --> 00:31:49,331
and together we will bring Go Won Pyo down.

408
00:31:51,130 --> 00:31:53,500
I thought you would be grief stricken,

409
00:31:55,170 --> 00:31:57,670
but I guess I do not know you enough.

410
00:31:58,301 --> 00:31:59,970
Will you be on my side?

411
00:32:02,841 --> 00:32:05,040
There is something I want to ask.

412
00:32:06,741 --> 00:32:09,051
If you wish to proceed with your plan,

413
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:14,051
what will you do with General Go?

414
00:32:17,021 --> 00:32:19,190
What if the two families of the Go's...

415
00:32:19,861 --> 00:32:21,730
shed blood?

416
00:32:22,031 --> 00:32:23,630
I trust Master Go.

417
00:32:25,561 --> 00:32:27,670
He is different from his father.

418
00:32:47,591 --> 00:32:50,591
I thought I would catch up with you at the hill if I hurried.

419
00:32:51,320 --> 00:32:54,391
But what are you doing here? Where is the Princess?

420
00:32:55,190 --> 00:32:57,431
- She left first. - Is that so?

421
00:32:59,031 --> 00:33:00,831
Then you must have been waiting for me.

422
00:33:01,570 --> 00:33:03,371
There is nothing I want to talk about with you.

423
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:04,700
That is a shame.

424
00:33:09,040 --> 00:33:10,910
But my sword has a lot to ask you.

425
00:33:22,591 --> 00:33:25,660
I will keep you updated regarding the King and the Crown Prince.

426
00:33:26,220 --> 00:33:28,560
I will secretly help with your plan,

427
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:30,730
so entrust it with me.

428
00:33:30,730 --> 00:33:32,160
I appreciate it.

429
00:33:33,360 --> 00:33:37,201
I feel like I have finally found a friend in the Capital.

430
00:33:37,540 --> 00:33:39,470
I am flattered, Your Highness.

431
00:33:49,910 --> 00:33:52,521
If you go back to the King and tell him the truth,

432
00:33:52,620 --> 00:33:54,220
I will spare your life.

433
00:33:54,691 --> 00:33:58,620
But if you keep pretending to be the Princess' husband,

434
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:01,391
I will end your life here.

435
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:02,990
I pity you.

436
00:34:04,831 --> 00:34:07,331
You do not want to admit that you lost Ga Jin.

437
00:34:07,600 --> 00:34:09,271
That must be why you want to behead me.

438
00:34:09,571 --> 00:34:10,701
Shut your mouth.

439
00:34:11,271 --> 00:34:12,870
Go ahead and kill me.

440
00:34:13,870 --> 00:34:15,670
Even if I die,

441
00:34:16,441 --> 00:34:18,910
I will never give Ga Jin to you.

442
00:34:21,910 --> 00:34:22,980
All right then.

443
00:34:39,261 --> 00:34:41,730
I cannot waste my sword to kill someone as lowly as you.

444
00:34:44,170 --> 00:34:46,071
I will end your life with my trick instead.

445
00:34:51,040 --> 00:34:55,110
I think I have started to like you.

446
00:35:09,660 --> 00:35:10,761
Get up.

447
00:35:54,910 --> 00:35:56,271
How dare you...

448
00:35:56,910 --> 00:35:59,040
come at a general of Goguryeo...

449
00:35:59,341 --> 00:36:01,810
with the skills you gained from collecting herbs and hunting?

450
00:36:08,720 --> 00:36:10,490
Do not act up and come at me.

451
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:15,331
All right then. I will end your life here.

452
00:36:31,341 --> 00:36:33,040
- Get this! - Stop it!

453
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:39,321
Stop it, Dal.

454
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:52,160
There is something I need to talk about with Master Go.

455
00:37:00,571 --> 00:37:02,110
Do not dare to run away!

456
00:37:03,170 --> 00:37:04,610
It is over, Master Go.

457
00:37:04,980 --> 00:37:06,680
The royal wedding and the arranged marriage...

458
00:37:07,641 --> 00:37:09,081
are all over.

459
00:37:10,511 --> 00:37:12,951
- Let us go. - What do you mean it is over?

460
00:37:17,251 --> 00:37:18,591
What do you mean it is over?

461
00:37:22,560 --> 00:37:24,961
Did you ever give me a chance to start?

462
00:37:28,701 --> 00:37:29,970
It has been eight years.

463
00:37:32,901 --> 00:37:35,211
No, it has been longer than that.

464
00:37:38,281 --> 00:37:39,881
I have been longing and...

465
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:42,480
waiting for you.

466
00:37:44,651 --> 00:37:45,981
I have missed you a lot.

467
00:37:49,190 --> 00:37:50,690
But why did you...

468
00:37:53,420 --> 00:37:57,190
tell me to give up before I even had a chance?

469
00:37:57,690 --> 00:37:59,060
Why? Why did you?

470
00:37:59,430 --> 00:38:01,471
It is not something we started.

471
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:06,371
Our fates have been twisted for so long...

472
00:38:08,511 --> 00:38:10,511
that neither of us can untangle them.

473
00:38:14,241 --> 00:38:15,680
I will untangle them.

474
00:38:15,881 --> 00:38:19,320
I will remove anything that comes between us!

475
00:38:19,320 --> 00:38:20,950
- So please... - Master Go!

476
00:38:22,590 --> 00:38:24,290
It is all over now.

477
00:38:27,590 --> 00:38:29,160
I need to leave now.

478
00:38:43,271 --> 00:38:46,440
I am sorry, Master Go.

479
00:39:16,410 --> 00:39:18,281
The Princess of Goguryeo, Princess Pyeonggang,

480
00:39:18,641 --> 00:39:21,141
was kicked out because she incited the wrath of the King.

481
00:39:22,180 --> 00:39:24,281
Since the arranged marriage came to a fail,

482
00:39:24,781 --> 00:39:28,550
I will write to you again once I find out what Go Won Pyo...

483
00:39:28,851 --> 00:39:31,460
cooks up for a scheme.

484
00:39:46,271 --> 00:39:47,670
General Go!

485
00:39:49,511 --> 00:39:52,741
General Go! What happened?

486
00:39:52,741 --> 00:39:54,511
Bring me some medicines.

487
00:39:55,851 --> 00:39:59,820
I cannot go back to the palace in this state.

488
00:40:00,351 --> 00:40:01,721
General Go!

489
00:40:18,641 --> 00:40:20,971
What will you tell the people of Ghost Valley?

490
00:40:21,670 --> 00:40:22,971
Do not worry.

491
00:40:24,070 --> 00:40:25,881
I will tell them that this all happened...

492
00:40:26,210 --> 00:40:28,710
because of the royal wedding, and that our marriage is not true.

493
00:40:30,781 --> 00:40:32,251
What if they find out?

494
00:40:32,881 --> 00:40:34,021
What?

495
00:40:34,021 --> 00:40:35,950
People from the Castle...

496
00:40:35,950 --> 00:40:38,660
might come and spy on us to see if we are a married couple.

497
00:40:38,660 --> 00:40:41,330
What will you do if they find out we are not a real couple?

498
00:40:41,330 --> 00:40:43,460
Hey, then we can pretend to be living...

499
00:40:47,560 --> 00:40:48,930
Should we live together?

500
00:40:49,501 --> 00:40:52,101
This is about us, not anyone else.

501
00:40:52,101 --> 00:40:53,501
I know.

502
00:40:54,570 --> 00:40:57,271
I am your husband, and you are my wife.

503
00:40:58,540 --> 00:40:59,940
What is he saying?

504
00:41:02,281 --> 00:41:04,511
- Ga Jin. - What?

505
00:41:05,981 --> 00:41:07,221
Let us do that.

506
00:41:09,251 --> 00:41:12,090
We can tell the villagers that we got married.

507
00:41:13,460 --> 00:41:15,231
That way, people from the Castle will not be able to find out.

508
00:41:18,830 --> 00:41:20,231
But this does not count as a real marriage.

509
00:41:20,501 --> 00:41:24,031
Why not? Am I not good enough as your husband?

510
00:41:24,031 --> 00:41:25,440
Darn you!

511
00:41:29,511 --> 00:41:33,040
It does not matter if it is real or not.

512
00:41:35,881 --> 00:41:37,781
As long as I can be with you...

513
00:41:40,251 --> 00:41:41,690
and protect you.

514
00:42:18,820 --> 00:42:20,790
My father was Daemodal...

515
00:42:21,460 --> 00:42:23,160
and a Widudehyeong.

516
00:42:23,891 --> 00:42:26,960
I am the son of General On Hyeop, the 17th chief of the Sunno Tribe,

517
00:42:27,901 --> 00:42:29,531
My name is On Dal.

518
00:42:36,371 --> 00:42:37,570
On Hyeop,

519
00:42:39,741 --> 00:42:42,310
you are tormenting me even after your death?

520
00:43:02,700 --> 00:43:05,040
I knew this would happen!

521
00:43:05,040 --> 00:43:07,401
So the rumour about the Princess being kicked out of the palace...

522
00:43:07,401 --> 00:43:08,511
must be true!

523
00:43:08,641 --> 00:43:10,611
- I guess so. - You just found that out?

524
00:43:10,611 --> 00:43:13,881
Did she really get married to the son of a merchant?

525
00:43:13,881 --> 00:43:17,450
Are you kidding me? I hear he is a fool.

526
00:43:17,710 --> 00:43:21,221
I hear he is a total idiot.

527
00:43:22,391 --> 00:43:25,221
I have never heard of that. My gosh.

528
00:43:25,320 --> 00:43:29,031
That must be why the King was infuriated.

529
00:43:30,261 --> 00:43:32,160
It is certain that the royal wedding has been cancelled.

530
00:43:33,361 --> 00:43:35,101
I think she was kicked out of the palace last night,

531
00:43:35,830 --> 00:43:36,871
but I have not found out her whereabouts.

532
00:43:36,871 --> 00:43:40,771
She must have gone to the village of the herb gatherer.

533
00:43:41,741 --> 00:43:43,611
Then the guy she got married to...

534
00:43:43,741 --> 00:43:46,040
Ga Jin is helping me.

535
00:43:47,080 --> 00:43:48,151
Sorry?

536
00:43:48,151 --> 00:43:50,751
We would have definitely run into Ga Jin...

537
00:43:50,751 --> 00:43:52,851
if we went into the palace.

538
00:43:53,550 --> 00:43:55,590
She left at the right time.

539
00:43:55,790 --> 00:43:57,521
Should I still tail her?

540
00:43:57,521 --> 00:43:58,891
Leave her be.

541
00:44:00,660 --> 00:44:03,131
When we see full moons several times...

542
00:44:03,460 --> 00:44:06,060
and when the stars shine in different places,

543
00:44:06,861 --> 00:44:08,971
she will come back herself.

